    "feat": {
        "name": "Five-breath Vanguard Dedication",
        "type": "stat_block_section",
        "subtype": "feat",
        "text": "You flow like the elemental cycle, adapting your stance and techniques constantly in response to whatever circumstances you face. You gain the Cycle Elemental Stance action.   \n  \n**Activate** Cycle Elemental Stance;",
